<div class="title">Guide to Brewing Ayahuasca</div>
<div class="substance">Huasca Brew (Syrian Rue & M. tenuiflora)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=MindFuck&Exact=1">MindFuck</a></div>


